an american essential for a buck you can certainly toss this in with whatever else you 're ordering this trip . rwe is one of the great articulators of the american mind . for better or worse , here 's a distilled vision of what we think . rwe 's positive and powerful view of human thought can be uplifting , though some may occasionally experience a desire to snort & quot ; oh , puh-lease ! & quot ; a great source of pithy quotes and sharp insights , rwe also provides considerable depth if you wade all the way into his works . everyone should have some collection of emerson on the shelf , and this collection hits all the high points ( though it is not , it should be said , a good choice for those suffering from chronic eyestrain )